title: "layout-columns"
description: "Multi-column text flow with measure constraints, column breaks, and vertical rhythm. Handles responsive column layout as a pure CSS layer — no JavaScript required."
elementName: layout-columns
category: custom
currentPath: /docs/elements/custom-elements/layout-columns/
permalink: /docs/elements/custom-elements/layout-columns/
